notes.title: Friend's Birthday
notes.details: This birthday I wish you and your family abundance, happiness, and health. May lady luck come especially for the birthday boy.

notes.title: Order a pizza
notes.details: Order a large size pizza. It should be Fajita flavour with fries and cold Drink.

notes.title: Search for internship
notes.details: Search for an internship in MERN stack and start working.

notes.title: Pay your gym fees
notes.details: Pay your gym fees on time before 10th of this month.
